videos.headline: Thomas strolls in for UNLV score
videos.description: Lexington Thomas runs it in for a 14-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Owens rips off 67-yard run
videos.description: Tyrone Owens breaks off long run and sets up the Lobos in the red zone.

videos.headline: Jordan takes option pitch in for score
videos.description: Romell Jordan runs in for an 8-yard touchdown for New Mexico's first score.

videos.headline: Chestnut plunges in for TD
videos.description: Daryl Chestnut runs it in for a one-yard score and the Lobos take the lead.

videos.headline: Thomas sprints his way for TD
videos.description: UNLV's Lexington Thomas runs through a hole big enough for a truck to drive through and does the rest with his legs for the 60-yard score.

videos.headline: Rogers goes untouched for UNLV TD
videos.description: QB Armani Rogers sprints his way for 83-yard touchdown and extend the Rebels lead.

videos.headline: Jordan calls his own number for Lobos TD
videos.description: QB Lamar Jordan keeps it on the option and sprints in for a 40-yard score.

videos.headline: Chestnut's big run sets up Lobos' TD
videos.description: Daryl Chestnut sprints for a big 35-yard run that leads to a rushing touchdown on the next play.

videos.headline: Jordan puts Lobos in front
videos.description: QB Lamar Jordan takes off for a 41-yard New Mexico score.
